{"title":"jenkins_categories_help","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"markdown":"In order to filter by **category**, please use the search box on top. Use the following query:
* `job_name:*<search_string>*`: `<search_string>` should be what you are looking for, e.g. `distribution-test`.

Wildcards allow to filter those job names that contains the category we are looking for.

**IMPORTANT**: `Categories` in widgets are based on Jenkins `installer` field, so may be not accurate to represent what you could expect as categories.


[See complete panel documentation](https://chaoss.github.io/grimoirelab-sigils/panels/jenkins-job-categories)"},"aggs":[]}
